<p>My oyster silk harem pants and oatmeal cashmere are perfect lounging. Comfy never looked so elegant.</p>

<p><img src="/images/malta/domus-zamittello/domus-zamittello-12.jpg" alt="domus-zamittello-12.jpg" /></p>

